\c 1
\s Amalungiselelo okunqoba ilizwe lamaKhanani
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kokufa kukaMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma kuJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, inceku kaMozisi, isithi\x + Eks. 24.13. Dute. 1.38.\x*:
\v 2 UMozisi inceku yami usefile\x + Dute. 34.5.\x*; ngakho-ke sukuma uchaphe le iJordani, wena labo bonke lababantu, liye elizweni engibanika lona, ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli.
\v 3 Yonke indawo lapho ingaphansi yonyawo lwenu ezanyathela khona ngilinike yona\x + Dute. 11.24. Josh. 14.9.\x*, njengokutsho kwami kuMozisi\x + Dute. 11.24. Josh. 14.9.\x*.
\v 4 Kusukela enkangala\x + Gen. 15.18. Eks. 23.31. Nani 34.3-12.\x* lale iLebhanoni kuze kufike emfuleni omkhulu, umfula iYufrathi\x + Dute. 3.25.\x*, ilizwe lonke lamaHethi, njalo kufike elwandle olukhulu lapho okutshona khona ilanga, kuzakuba ngumngcele wenu.
\v 5 Kakulamuntu ozakuma phambi kwakho zonke izinsuku zempilo yakho\x + Dute. 7.24; Josh. 10.8.\x*. Njengalokhu ngangiloMozisi\x + 1.17; Eks. 3.12.\x*, ngizakuba lawe\x + Dute. 31.8,23. Josh. 1.9,17. Josh. 3.7. Josh. 6.27. Hlu. 2.18. 6.12. Isa. 43.2,5.\x*; kangiyikukutshiya, kangiyikukulahla\x + Dute. 31.6,8. 1 Lan. 28.20. Heb. 13.5.\x*.
\v 6 Qina, ume isibindi, ngoba wena uzakwenza lababantu badle ilifa lelizwe engalifungela oyise ukubanika lona\x + 1.7,9,18. Dute. 31.6.\x*.
\v 7 Kuphela qina, ube lesibindi esikhulu\x + 1.7,9,18. Dute. 31.6.\x*, ukugcina ukwenza ngokomlayo wonke uMozisi inceku yami akulaya wona\x + 11.15.\x*; ungaphambuki kuwo uye ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo, ukuze uphumelele loba ngaphi lapho oya khona\x + Dute. 5.32.\x*.
\v 8 Ugwalo lwalumlayo lungasuki emlonyeni wakho, kodwa uzindle kuwo emini lebusuku, ukuze uqaphele ukwenza njengakho konke okubhaliweyo kulo\x + Hlab. 1.2.\x*, ngoba khona uzakwenza indlela yakho iphumelele, ubusuphumelela.
\v 9 Kangikulayanga yini? Qina, ume isibindi\x + 1.6,7,18.\x*; ungesabi\x + Dute. 1.29. 7.21. 20.3. 31. 6.\x*, ungatshaywa luvalo\x + Dute. 31.8.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ilawe loba ngaphi lapho oya khona\x + 1.7.\x*.
\p
\v 10 UJoshuwa waselaya izinduna zabantu, esithi\x + 3.2. 8.33. 23.2. 24.1. Dute. 16.18.\x*:
\v 11 Dabulani phakathi kwenkamba lilaye abantu lithi: Zilungiseleni umphako, ngoba kusesezinsuku ezintathu lizachapha le iJordani, ukuze lingene lidle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elinika lona ukuthi lidle ilifa lalo\x + 3.2. Dute. 11.31.\x*.
\p
\v 12 UJoshuwa wasekhuluma kwabakoRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase esithi:
\v 13 Khumbulani ilizwi uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* alilaya ngalo esithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu iyaliphumuza, ilinika lelilizwe\x + Nani 32.20-28.\x*.
\v 14 Omkenu, abantwanyana benu, lezifuyo zenu kuzahlala elizweni uMozisi alinika lona nganeno kweJordani; kodwa lina lizachapha lihlomile phambi kwabafowenu, wonke amaqhawe alamandla, libasize,
\v 15 iN\nd kosi\nd* ize iphumuze abafowenu njengani, labo njalo badle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ebanika lona\x + Nani 32.20-28.\x*. Lizabuyela-ke elizweni lelifa lenu, lidle ilifa lalo, uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* alinika lona, nganeno kweJordani, empumalanga\x + 22.4.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Basebemphendula uJoshuwa besithi: Konke osilaya khona sizakwenza, laloba ngaphi lapho ozasithuma khona sizahamba.
\v 17 Njengakho konke esamlalela uMozisi ngakho, ngokunjalo sizakulalela. Kuphela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ibe lawe njengoba yayiloMozisi\x + 1.5. 1 Sam. 20.13. 1 Kho. 1.37.\x*.
\v 18 Wonke umuntu ozavukela umlomo wakho, angalaleli amazwi akho, kukho konke omlaya khona, uzabulawa\x + Dute. 1.26.\x*. Kuphela qina, ume isibindi\x + 1.6,7,9.\x*.